1966
01:44:07.578 --> 01:44:09.308
Sekarang... ambil foto saat
aku pura-pura mati.


1967
01:44:09.380 --> 01:44:10.507
Seperti ini.

1968
01:44:11.582 --> 01:44:12.641
Sebentar!

1969
01:44:14.352 --> 01:44:15.820
