Aku hanya manusia!


2079
01:49:13.450 --> 01:49:14.474
Sunita...

2080
01:49:26.430 --> 01:49:27.363
Ayah!

2081
01:49:27.931 --> 01:49:28.990
Yah!

2082
01:49:50.187 --> 01:49:52.156
